Definition: coupling that connects two rotating shafts allowing freedom of movement in all directions
Example: in motor vehicles a universal joint allows the driveshaft to move up and down as the vehicle passes over bumps
Synonyms: universal, coupling, drive_line, p, that, connects, two, rotating, shafts, allowing, freedom, of, movement, in, all, directions, motor, vehicles, a, joint, allows, the, driveshaft, to, move, up, and, down, as, vehicle, passes, over, bumps
Category: noun.artifact
